node.text:
Comment “I’m building wealth” if you agree. 🙋🏻‍♀️🤑I have been able to create 5 different streams of income in the last 2 years.⬇️

To become financially successful, you need more than one source of income.

If you have several sources of income, you will get that much closer to becoming financially independent.

Do you know that an average millionaire has at least 7 streams of income? 😮

Building passive income streams is not easy because it takes a lot of time, effort and systems. However, if successfully built, working becomes optional. It is indeed a great channel to building wealth .

I have been able to create 5 different streams of income in the last 2 years and currently working on adding 2 more this year. 

Here are a few ideas if you want to build an additional stream of income and some of the ones I have personally utilized.

𝟏. 𝐒𝐭𝐚𝐫𝐭 𝐚𝐧 𝐎𝐧𝐥𝐢𝐧𝐞 𝐛𝐮𝐬𝐢𝐧𝐞𝐬𝐬 
𝟐. 𝐒𝐞𝐥𝐥 𝐚𝐧 𝐞𝐛𝐨𝐨𝐤 
𝟑. 𝐃𝐢𝐠𝐢𝐭𝐚𝐥 𝐜𝐨𝐮𝐫𝐬𝐞𝐬 
𝟑. 𝐀𝐟𝐟𝐢𝐥𝐢𝐚𝐭𝐞 𝐦𝐚𝐫𝐤𝐞𝐭𝐢𝐧𝐠 
𝟒. 𝐌𝐨𝐧𝐞𝐭𝐢𝐳𝐢𝐧𝐠 𝐦𝐲 𝐈𝐧𝐬𝐭𝐚𝐠𝐫𝐚𝐦 
𝟓. 𝐒𝐞𝐫𝐯𝐢𝐜𝐞𝐬/𝐜𝐨𝐚𝐜𝐡𝐢𝐧𝐠
6. Investments
7. Blogging 
8. Amazon FBA
9. Rental properties
10. Network Marketing 
11. Freelancing 
12. Sell on Etsy 
14. Dropshipping

Dm me “IG Blueprint” if you want to learn how to monetize your Instagram and create multiple streams of income like 1-5 above. 🤑

I generated 100k in 6 months with digital products and affiliate marketing all through Instagram with no Ads and no email list.

If I can do it SO CAN YOU.

If I can grow a community on Instagram from 0 to 800K+ in 2years without knowing anything about Instagram before I started SO CAN YOU. 

If I can create an ebook, digital courses, and teach SO CAN YOU. 

If I can use my platform to advertise other women entrepreneurs to help them grow their business SO CAN YOU. 

If I can make money with affiliate marketing promoting other people's products that I truly believe in SO CAN YOU.
